      "amount": "1 tsp",
      "notes": "grated, for garnish"
    },
    {
      "name": "olive oil",
      "amount": "1 tsp",
      "notes": "for sautéing"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a non-stick pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add zucchini slices and cook for 3-4 minutes per side, until tender and lightly browned.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together soy sauce, rice vinegar, and Shu sauce.",
    "Pour sauce over zucchini and toss to coat.",
    "Sprinkle with chopped scallions and grated mu.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
